dct_title_s: Map of Tiffin River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Tiffin River Basin
dct_description_sm: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Tiffin Basin and the quality of underground water.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water, from data compiled by Lawrence R. Brunstetter".
